{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4579d5ff76","title":"右派言论——诬蔑镇压反革命运动","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9590c59910","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"4579d5ff76"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"023f8c79dd","name":"郭振淮"},{"id":"55d4e5b786","name":"中国人民大学"},{"id":"78996e9f1b","name":"孙国梅"},{"id":"dadcfe1139","name":"朱华荣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6b5c95e671","type":"title","text":"右派言论——诬蔑镇压反革命运动","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"58128d88d1","type":"authors","text":"中国人民大学朱华荣孙国梅郭振淮","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"451f6c35fb","type":"paragraph","text":"“镇反杀反革命77万多人，太多了，过去历代王朝都没有一下子杀这么多。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"e74f528661","type":"paragraph","text":"“镇反时杀人如麻，刑场上到处是尸体。”（中国人民大学法律系助教  朱华荣）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"2de9919cce","type":"paragraph","text":"“镇反是一个‘报复’，是因为国民党过去打了你们，你们现在要报复”。他同情和怜悯反革命分子，他认为“年青的反革命可以不抓。可以让他们劳动改造。”（中国人民大学历史系助教  孙国梅的材料）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"5accbf883f","type":"paragraph","text":"“各次运动的偏差和错误不是个别的，而是普遍的，不是从团结出发，而是从整人出发。肃反运动偏差是社会问题，不是从团结愿望出发，达到团结目的，造成压力，成绩少、缺点错误多。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"c0a93295b2","type":"paragraph","text":"社会上有千千万万人受到迫害，在社会上被错斗了多少人，这是个社会问题。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"cc466b88bf","type":"paragraph","text":"过去各次运动都是整人，时代过去了，我们应该吸取教训。”（中国人民大学计划系讲师  郭振淮）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"},{"id":"f0409623c1","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76"}],"page":{"id":"08edf1539d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4579d5ff76","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}